        "---\n",
        "title: Sternoclavicular Joint (SCJ)\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "![Sternoclavicular joint (Anterior view) @grayAnatomyHumanBody1918](/The Archive/Images/Gray anatomy 1918 images/Syndesmology/image325 gray1918 Sternoclavicular articulation. Anterior view.gif){#fig-gray1918-image325}\n",
        "\n",
        "<!-- \n",
        "to do:\n",
